         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 1773, recto: (1) By this place, by its power, (2) as to the whole inheritance (3) of my parents, I do not deceive (4) you even to the value of a half- (5) tremis, and I do not ---, (6) ever, regarding my share of the yard (7) with Matthew.  If I do not relinquish (8) it to you, (9) may it be given(?) as an offering (10) on my behalf(?).</ab>
